ent000000;Arial,sans-serif;">Christmas Day</span></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></div><p><meta charset="utf-8"></p><p dir="ltr"><span style="background-color:transparent000000;Arial,sans-serif;">The Maharashtra government's holiday calendar for 2026 captures the state's lively spirit and mix of cultures. It highlights fun festivals like Ganesh Chaturthi and Diwali, as well as critical national days.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr"><span style="background-color:transparent000000;Arial,sans-serif;">This mix of holidays lets workers, students, and families fit in their own special events throughout the year, helping everyone enjoy a good work-life balance and some joy in every season.</span></p><p dir="ltr"><span style="background-color:transparent000000;"><strong>Related Articles:</strong></span><br><span style="background-color:transparent000000;">1. </span><a href="https://cleartax.in/s/maharashtra-government-holiday-list-2025" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span style="background-color:transparent000000;">Maharashtra Government Holiday​s List 2025</span></a><br><span style="background-color:transparent000000;">2. </span><a href="https://cleartax.in/s/tamil-nadu-government-holidays-list-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span style="background-color:transparent000000;">Tamil Nadu Government Holidays 2026</span></a><br><span style="background-color:transparent000000;">3. </span><a href="https://cleartax.in/s/karnataka-governmnet-holidays-list-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span style="background-color:transparent000000;">Karnataka Government Holidays List 2026</span></a><br><span style="background-color:transparent000000;">4. </span><a href="https://cleartax.in/s/telangana-government-holiday-list-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span style="background-color:transparent000000;">Telangana Government Holidays List 2026</span></a><br>5. <a href="https://cleartax.in/s/punjab-government-holiday-list-2026" target=